Subject: [PATCH] Include implicit headers for gcc-16

New GCC release in the horizon, more implicit includes removed.

This reverts some include removals in
7c7241441d0c96b4d69e84c38c745612db8b22b7
234ad1bf8aee61d5c5e0d8de9d057b8b41bd01c7

Bug: https://bugs.gentoo.org/960304
Signed-off-by: Alfred Wingate <parona@protonmail.com>
